{
  "text": "In a \"close encounter\" by a Confederation type of craft I assume that this \"close encounter\" is with a thought-form type of craft. Do Wanderers within the past few years have \"close encounters\" with landed thought-form type of craft? I am Ra. This has occurred although it is much less common than the Orion type of so-called \"close encounter. \" We may note that in a universe of unending unity the concept of a \"close encounter\" is humorous, for are not all encounters of a nature of self with self? Therefore, how can any encounter be less than very, very close?",
